&lt;/article&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><author>processone</author><guid isPermaLink="false">https://github.com/processone/ejabberd</guid><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2020 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>benoitc/erlang-metrics #2 in Erlang, This week</title><link>https://github.com/benoitc/erlang-metrics</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;A generic interface to different metrics systems in Erlang.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div id="readme" class="md" data-path="README.md"&gt;&lt;article class="markdown-body entry-content p-5" itemprop="text"&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-metrics-a-generic-interface-to-different-metrics-systems-in-erlang" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#metrics-a-generic-interface-to-different-metrics-systems-in-erlang"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;metrics: A generic interface to different metrics systems in Erlang.&lt;/h1&gt;
