&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Version:&lt;/strong&gt; 2.5.0&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-metrics" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#metrics"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;metrics&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A generic interface to folsom, exometer, grapherl or any compliant interface. This
application has been extracted from
&lt;a href="https://github.com/benoitc/hackney"&gt;hackney&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Currently supported backend are:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/folsom-project/folsom"&gt;Folsom&lt;/a&gt;: &lt;code&gt;metrics_folsom&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/Feuerlabs/exometer"&gt;Exometer&lt;/a&gt;: &lt;code&gt;metrics_exometer&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you need the support for another backend, please &lt;a href="https://github.com/benoitc/erlang-metrics/issues"&gt;open a ticket&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://hex.pm/packages/metrics" rel="nofollow"&gt;&lt;img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/c06191f8e9f2e61e582519839dcebace736690c5/687474703a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f686578706d2f762f6d6574726963732e7376673f7374796c653d666c6174" alt="Hex pm" data-canonical-src="http://img.shields.io/hexpm/v/metrics.svg?style=flat" style="max-width:100%;"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-usage" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#usage"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Usage&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-set-a-backend" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#set-a-backend"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Set a backend&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The backend can be set in the application environment using the &lt;code&gt;metrics_mod&lt;/code&gt; setting or using &lt;code&gt;metrics:backend/1&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-register-a-new-metric" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#register-a-new-metric"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;register a new metric:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;metrics:new(counter, "c").
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Depending on the backend the following metrics types can be passed: counter | histogram | gauge | meter | spiral&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-update-a-metric" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#update-a-metric"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;update a metric&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A counter can simply be incremented by 1 using &lt;code&gt;metrics:update/1&lt;/code&gt;. or by passing a positive or negative integer like this:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;metrics:update("c", {c, 1}).
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Other metrics are updated via &lt;code&gt;metrics:update/2&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-example" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#example"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Example:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight highlight-source-erlang"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class="pl-c1"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="pl-k"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="pl-en"&gt;application&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class="pl-en"&gt;ensure_all_started&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span class="pl-c1"&gt;metrics&lt;/span&gt;).
{&lt;span class="pl-c1"&gt;ok&lt;/span&gt;,[&lt;span class="pl-c1"&gt;metrics&lt;/span&gt;]}
&lt;span class="pl-c1"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="pl-k"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="pl-en"&gt;application&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class="pl-en"&gt;ensure_all_started&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span class="pl-c1"&gt;folsom&lt;/span&gt;).
{&lt;span class="pl-c1"&gt;ok&lt;/span&gt;,[&lt;span class="pl-c1"&gt;bear&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;span class="pl-c1"&gt;folsom&lt;/span&gt;]}
&lt;span class="pl-c1"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="pl-k"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="pl-en"&gt;metrics&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class="pl-en"&gt;backend&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span class="pl-c1"&gt;metrics_folsom&lt;/span&gt;).
&lt;span class="pl-c1"&gt;ok&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="pl-c1"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="pl-k"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="pl-en"&gt;metrics&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class="pl-en"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span class="pl-c1"&gt;counter&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class="pl-s"&gt;&lt;span class="pl-pds"&gt;"&lt;/span&gt;c&lt;span class="pl-pds"&gt;"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;).
&lt;span class="pl-c1"&gt;ok&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="pl-c1"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="pl-k"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="pl-en"&gt;metrics&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class="pl-en"&gt;update&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span class="pl-s"&gt;&lt;span class="pl-pds"&gt;"&lt;/span&gt;c&lt;span class="pl-pds"&gt;"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;).
&lt;span class="pl-c1"&gt;ok&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="pl-c1"&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="pl-k"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="pl-en"&gt;folsom_metrics&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class="pl-en"&gt;get_metric_value&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span class="pl-s"&gt;&lt;span class="pl-pds"&gt;"&lt;/span&gt;c&lt;span class="pl-pds"&gt;"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;).
&lt;span class="pl-c1"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="pl-c1"&gt;7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="pl-k"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="pl-en"&gt;metrics&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class="pl-en"&gt;update&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span class="pl-s"&gt;&lt;span class="pl-pds"&gt;"&lt;/span&gt;c&lt;span class="pl-pds"&gt;"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;, {&lt;span class="pl-c1"&gt;c&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class="pl-c1"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;}).
&lt;span class="pl-c1"&gt;ok&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="pl-c1"&gt;8&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="pl-k"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="pl-en"&gt;folsom_metrics&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class="pl-en"&gt;get_metric_value&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span class="pl-s"&gt;&lt;span class="pl-pds"&gt;"&lt;/span&gt;c&lt;span class="pl-pds"&gt;"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;).
&lt;span class="pl-c1"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-documentation" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#documentation"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Documentation&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Full doc is available in the &lt;a href="http://github.com/benoitc/erlang-metrics/blob/master/doc/metrics.md"&gt;&lt;code&gt;metrics&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt; module.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-build" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#build"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Build&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;$ rebar3 compile
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-modules" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#modules"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Modules&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;table width="100%" border="0" summary="list of modules"&gt;
&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="http://github.com/benoitc/erlang-metrics/blob/master/doc/metrics.md"&gt;metrics&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="http://github.com/benoitc/erlang-metrics/blob/master/doc/metrics_exometer.md"&gt;metrics_exometer&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;a href="http://github.com/benoitc/erlang-metrics/blob/master/doc/metrics_folsom.md"&gt;metrics_folsom&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;
